      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ARMATREE JUDO (7) recorded a win over 431m at this track in an outstanding 24.74 last start. In form and looks the one to beat again. VICTOR CARGO (2) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 1.75 lengths back in third (24.87) at this track in a Grade 5 over 431m. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Hard to beat again. RED ROCK LOTUS (8) was well supported last start but didn't deliver when fourth (18.54), beaten 4 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. A big run wouldn't surprise. DANNY KEEPING (1) is in the mix despite finishing out of the placings here last start.",
